<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-30 14:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5221 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOSTON-REAL-2TAKES-NY     01-30 0742
