</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SLAPPING-SADDAM-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TO HURT SADDAM, HELP HIS PEOPLE  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
